title: The Morning After My 48 Hour Bender
itunes:title: The Morning After My 48 Hour Bender
description: It's the morning after a HUGE playoff win against the Bucs! Kelly is in the studio, straight off the plane, to talk about her game day experience in Tampa, hot takes on some trending football topics, some hilarious stories from her weekend bender and more of the story of her & Matthew!The Morning After podcast is produced by ACTIONPARK MEDIA. Follow us on Social Media:@actionparkmediagroup @kbstafford89@themorningafter.kellystafford
